snippet.title: Elflock - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Here's your look at Elflock in this trailer for this upcoming cinematic UE5 single-player, third-person fantasy adventure game based on Hungarian folklore and medieval traditions. The Elflock trailer showcases gameplay as we learn more about the story. In Elflock, you are a princess returning to your home on the brink of war and it's up to you to navigate the machinations of the nobles surrounding the king. Engage in intricate dialogues and uncover mysteries in this branching fantasy tale. Elflock will be available on PC in 2025. You can learn more about the game on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3094690?utm_source=ign
